---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About | 24 Hour Journey"
  description="Learn about Skyzer Networks and our approach to building websites for small businesses and creators."
  url="https://24hourjourney.blog/about"
  image_preview="/icons/preview.png"
  type="website"
>

  <!-- TERMINAL INTRO -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="grid-lines"></div>
    <div class="about-hero-inner">
      <div class="terminal-block">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <span class="tb-dot tb-red"></span>
          <span class="tb-dot tb-yellow"></span>
          <span class="tb-dot tb-green"></span>
          <span class="tb-file">skyzer/about.md</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div class="t-line"><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">whoami</span></div>
          <div class="t-line t-out">Skyzer Networks — a two-person web agency</div>
          <div class="t-line t-out">building sites for small businesses &amp; creators.</div>
          <div class="t-line t-blank">&nbsp;</div>
          <div class="t-line"><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">cat mission.txt</span></div>
          <div class="t-line t-out">We believe every small business deserves</div>
          <div class="t-line t-out">a website that actually works for them —</div>
          <div class="t-line t-out">not just something that exists.</div>
          <div class="t-line t-blank">&nbsp;</div>
          <div class="t-line"><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd blink">_</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-hero-text">
        <div class="about-eyebrow">The story behind the name</div>
        <h1 class="about-title">Built by people<br/><span class="about-title-accent">who actually care.</span></h1>
        <p class="about-lead">Skyzer Networks isn't a faceless studio. It's two people — Michael and Matt — who got tired of seeing small businesses stuck with outdated, ineffective websites and decided to do something about it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ORIGIN SECTION -->
  <section class="origin-section">
    <div class="origin-inner">
      <div class="origin-label">
        <span class="ol-num">001</span>
        <span class="ol-rule"></span>
        <span class="ol-text">Origin</span>
      </div>
      <div class="origin-content">
        <h2 class="origin-title">Why Skyzer Networks?</h2>
        <p class="origin-body">The name came first — and it stuck. Skyzer Networks. It felt like something that moved fast, connected things, and had its own energy. That turned out to be exactly the right fit: Michael had always had a talent for networking, for seeing how systems and people connect, and for understanding how the web links all of it together.</p>
        <p class="origin-body">From that moment, the direction was clear. Build something that uses those instincts — not just technically, but creatively — to help the businesses and creators who need it most.</p>
        <div class="origin-stat-row">
          <div class="o-stat">
            <div class="o-stat-num">2</div>
            <div class="o-stat-label">Founders</div>
          </div>
          <div class="o-stat">
            <div class="o-stat-num">100%</div>
            <div class="o-stat-label">Independent</div>
          </div>
          <div class="o-stat">
            <div class="o-stat-num">0</div>
            <div class="o-stat-label">Corporate fluff</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TEAM -->
  <section class="team-section">
    <div class="team-inner">
      <div class="team-label">
        <span class="ol-num">002</span>
        <span class="ol-rule"></span>
        <span class="ol-text">The Team</span>
      </div>

      <!-- MICHAEL -->
      <div class="founder-card founder-michael">
        <div class="fc-sidebar">
          <div class="fc-avatar fc-avatar-m">
            <span class="fc-initials">MY</span>
            <div class="fc-avatar-ring"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fc-role-tag">Co-Founder &amp; Lead Designer</div>
          <div class="fc-handles">
            <span class="fc-handle">@michaelyurachek</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fc-body">
          <div class="fc-name-row">
            <h2 class="fc-name">Michael Yurachek</h2>
            <div class="fc-badge fc-badge-blue">Design &amp; Dev</div>
          </div>

          <p class="fc-bio">Michael discovered code in his freshman year of high school and never looked back. What started as curiosity — figuring out how things are built on the web — quickly became something more: a genuine love for design. Not just aesthetics, but the craft of making something that looks intentional, feels smooth, and actually communicates something.</p>

          <p class="fc-bio">That early instinct for how things connect carried into everything else. Networking isn't just a technical skill for Michael — it's a way of thinking. Seeing how systems, people, and ideas link together. When the name "Skyzer" surfaced, it clicked instantly. It felt like the right container for everything he wanted to build.</p>

          <p class="fc-bio">Skyzer Networks is his attempt to make the thing he always wished existed: a web agency that brings real design thinking to small businesses who deserve it just as much as big ones do.</p>

          <div class="fc-skills">
            <div class="fcs-label">Strengths</div>
            <div class="fcs-tags">
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-blue">UI Design</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-blue">Front-End Dev</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-blue">Brand Identity</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-blue">Networking</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-blue">Systems Thinking</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="fc-quote">
            <span class="fcq-mark">"</span>
            I've loved design since the first time I opened a code editor. Everything since has just been building toward making that mean something for real people.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MATT -->
      <div class="founder-card founder-matt">
        <div class="fc-sidebar">
          <div class="fc-avatar fc-avatar-a">
            <span class="fc-initials">MS</span>
            <div class="fc-avatar-ring fc-avatar-ring-a"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fc-role-tag">Co-Founder &amp; Business Lead</div>
          <div class="fc-handles">
            <span class="fc-handle">@matthewsanders</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fc-body">
          <div class="fc-name-row">
            <h2 class="fc-name">Matt Sanders</h2>
            <div class="fc-badge fc-badge-amber">Growth &amp; Clients</div>
          </div>

          <p class="fc-bio">Matt has always been drawn to the business side of things. Give him a conversation about strategy, positioning, or how to reach the right people and he's completely in his element. When Michael brought him in as co-founder, it wasn't a hard sell — Matt saw immediately that this was something real and worth building.</p>

          <p class="fc-bio">His role at Skyzer is the connective tissue between great work and the people who need it. Marketing, client relationships, figuring out who the right audience is and how to talk to them — that's where Matt operates. He's the reason projects don't just look good on a screen but actually land for the clients who matter.</p>

          <p class="fc-bio">Matt loves discussing business almost as much as he loves being in the room where deals get done. That energy is exactly what a growing agency needs alongside strong technical work.</p>

          <div class="fc-skills">
            <div class="fcs-label">Strengths</div>
            <div class="fcs-tags">
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-amber">Marketing</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-amber">Client Relations</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-amber">Business Strategy</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-amber">Copywriting</span>
              <span class="fcs-tag fcs-amber">Growth</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="fc-quote">
            <span class="fcq-mark">"</span>
            The best websites aren't just well-built — they're well-positioned. My job is making sure the people who need Skyzer can actually find us and feel it.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="values-inner">
      <div class="values-label">
        <span class="ol-num">003</span>
        <span class="ol-rule"></span>
        <span class="ol-text">What We Believe</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="values-title">How we think about the work</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="val-card">
          <div class="val-num">01</div>
          <h3 class="val-name">Small businesses deserve real design</h3>
          <p class="val-desc">A local shop, a freelancer, a service provider — they all deserve a website that's as considered and crafted as any Fortune 500 brand. Budget constraints don't have to mean design compromises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card">
          <div class="val-num">02</div>
          <h3 class="val-name">Websites should work, not just exist</h3>
          <p class="val-desc">A site that looks nice but doesn't convert, confuses visitors, or takes forever to load isn't doing its job. We build with intent — every decision has a reason behind it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card">
          <div class="val-num">03</div>
          <h3 class="val-name">Honesty over hype</h3>
          <p class="val-desc">We're not going to promise the moon. We'll tell you what you need, what you don't, and what's actually going to move the needle — even if that's a harder conversation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card">
          <div class="val-num">04</div>
          <h3 class="val-name">Two people, fully invested</h3>
          <p class="val-desc">There's no account manager buffering your access to the people actually doing the work. When you work with Skyzer, you're working with Michael and Matt directly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <div class="cta-glow"></div>
      <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to work together?</h2>
      <p class="cta-sub">Whether you're starting from zero or fixing something that isn't working, we'd love to hear what you're building.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="https://skyzernetworks.com" class="cta-btn-primary">Visit skyzernetworks.com →</a>
        <a href="/posts" class="cta-btn-ghost">Read the blog first</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>

/* ── ABOUT HERO ── */
.about-hero {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--bg);
  margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
}

.grid-lines {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,200,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,200,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 48px 48px;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.about-hero-inner {
  max-width: 1160px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) 1.25rem clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 3rem;
}

/* Terminal */
.terminal-block {
  background: #080e16;
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(0,200,255,0.25);
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  font-family: 'Courier New', 'Lucida Console', monospace;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 480px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,200,255,0.06);
}

.terminal-bar {
  background: #0d1520;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(0,200,255,0.15);
  padding: 8px 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
}

.tb-dot {
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.tb-red    { background: #ff5f57; }
.tb-yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
.tb-green  { background: #28c840; }

.tb-file {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  margin-left: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
}

.terminal-body {
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
}

.t-line {
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: rgba(245,243,239,0.55);
}

.t-blank { line-height: 0.8; }

.t-prompt {
  color: var(--blue);
  margin-right: 8px;
  user-select: none;
}

.t-cmd { color: var(--white); }

.t-out { color: rgba(245,243,239,0.5); padding-left: 18px; }

.blink {
  animation: blink 1.1s step-end infinite;
  color: var(--blue);
}

@keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }

/* Hero text */
.about-hero-text {}

.about-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  color: var(--blue);
  letter-spacing: 2.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}

.about-eyebrow::before {
  content: '';
  width: 20px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--blue);
  display: inline-block;
}

.about-title {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-5xl);
  line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  color: var(--white);
}

.about-title-accent {
  display: block;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}

.about-lead {
  font-size: var(--text-md);
  color: rgba(245,243,239,0.6);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.75;
  max-width: 580px;
}

/* ── ORIGIN ── */
.origin-section {
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--mid);
}

.origin-inner {
  max-width: 1160px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) 1.25rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2rem;
}

.origin-label {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}

.ol-num {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  color: var(--blue);
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}

.ol-rule {
  flex: 1;
  height: 0.5px;
  background: var(--border);
  max-width: 40px;
}

.ol-text {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.origin-title {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.origin-body {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: rgba(245,243,239,0.6);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  max-width: 680px;
}

.origin-stat-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2.5rem;
  margin-top: 2rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.o-stat {}

.o-stat-num {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.o-stat-label {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* ── TEAM ── */
.team-section {
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
}

.team-inner {
  max-width: 1160px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) 1.25rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2.5rem;
}

.team-label {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}

/* Founder Cards */
.founder-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2rem;
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.founder-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1.5px;
}

.founder-michael::before {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), transparent);
}

.founder-matt::before {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffaa00, transparent);
}

/* Sidebar */
.fc-sidebar {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.fc-avatar {
  width: 64px;
  height: 64px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.fc-avatar-m {
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(0,200,255,0.2), rgba(0,200,255,0.05));
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,255,0.35);
}

.fc-avatar-a {
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,170,0,0.2), rgba(255,170,0,0.05));
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,170,0,0.35);
}

.fc-initials {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-2xl);
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1;
}

.fc-avatar-ring {
  position: absolute;
  inset: -5px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(0,200,255,0.15);
}

.fc-avatar-ring-a {
  border-color: rgba(255,170,0,0.15);
}

.fc-role-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.fc-handle {
  font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--blue);
}

/* Body */
.fc-name-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.fc-name {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--white);
}

.fc-badge {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.fc-badge-blue {
  background: rgba(0,200,255,0.08);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(0,200,255,0.3);
  color: var(--blue);
}

.fc-badge-amber {
  background: rgba(255,170,0,0.08);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(255,170,0,0.3);
  color: #ffaa00;
}

.fc-bio {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: rgba(245,243,239,0.6);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
}

/* Skills */
.fc-skills {
  margin: 1.25rem 0;
}

.fcs-label {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}

.fcs-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 6px;
}

.fcs-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.fcs-blue {
  background: rgba(0,200,255,0.06);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(0,200,255,0.2);
  color: rgba(0,200,255,0.85);
}

.fcs-amber {
  background: rgba(255,170,0,0.06);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(255,170,0,0.2);
  color: rgba(255,170,0,0.85);
}

/* Quote */
.fc-quote {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
  padding-left: 1rem;
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: rgba(245,243,239,0.45);
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}

.fcq-mark {
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 2rem;
  color: var(--border);
  line-height: 0;
  vertical-align: -0.5rem;
  margin-right: 2px;
}

/* ── VALUES ── */
.values-section {
  background: var(--mid);
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
}

.values-inner {
  max-width: 1160px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) 1.25rem;
}

.values-label {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.values-title {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  color: var(--white);
}

.values-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.val-card {
  padding: 1.75rem;
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  position: relative;
}

.val-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.val-num {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.val-name {
  font-family: var(--font-sub);
  font-size: var(--text-md);
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.val-desc {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: rgba(245,243,239,0.5);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.75;
}

/* ── CTA ── */
.about-cta {
  padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) 1.25rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-align: center;
}

.cta-inner {
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

.cta-glow {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 400px;
  height: 200px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0,200,255,0.07), transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.cta-title {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: var(--white);
}

.cta-sub {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: rgba(245,243,239,0.55);
  line-height: 1.75;
  font-weight: 300;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.cta-actions {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cta-btn-primary {
  background: var(--blue);
  color: #000;
